room_title: Escape room "Escape The Manor" by Unlock the Adventure in Titusville
room_description: There's a chill in the air and a storm is coming your way...better take shelter in the old manor on the hill! You and your group must work together and explore Dark Ghost Manor in this chilling adventure in the darkness! Get ready for a scary experience complete with fully-immersive puzzles and high-tech special effects! Come face to face with your fears and try your best to...Escape the Manor!
